Sentencas: The SOFC group at Forschungszentrum Juelich has assembled and tested more than 220 SOFC stacks during the last 10 years, rated between 100 W and 15 kW. The topics of high-performance materials, corrosion, materials compatibility, and cost-effectiveness, including manufacturing processes, etc., are being continuously addressed.
Titulo: Overview of the development of solid oxide fuel cells at Forschungszentrum Juelich

Sentencas: Large stacks of 5 kW and above have been operated since 2002 and have also been successfully delivered to other institutions.
Titulo: Overview of the development of solid oxide fuel cells at Forschungszentrum Juelich

Sentencas: In parallel, lightweight stacks have been developed in the cassette design line for SOFC-APU.
Titulo: Overview of the development of solid oxide fuel cells at Forschungszentrum Juelich

Sentencas: Several 1-20 kW SOFC laboratory systems are in preparation.
Titulo: Overview of the development of solid oxide fuel cells at Forschungszentrum Juelich
